page.title: 13LAW AND ORDER
page.content: Policing the area is organised from Havant.The building was built in 1966.At the Police Station they have six male cells and two female cells.If people have something wrong with them they go in the D.P.R mental health cells. They have one Police van, twelve mini buses, one volvo and nine panda cars.They only have one type of dog and that is the Alsatian,they have ten of these at the most.Also they have a lot of policemen and policewomen.They have one Detective Chief Inspector, three Detective Sgts.and eleven Detectives.They have one Superintendant on C.I.D, three Inspectors and nine Sgts.
